### [F3-SETUP] Create payments for user ID=2 (rider)
POST http://localhost:8085/api/payments
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
X-User-Id: 1
X-User-Role: ADMIN

{
  "rideId": 1,
  "userId": 2,
  "amount": 75.0,
  "status": "COMPLETED",
  "method": "CREDIT_CARD"
}

